text: Ayskaya () is a rural locality (a village) in Turnalinsky Selsoviet, Salavatsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 207 as of 2010. There are 3 streets. == Geography == It is located 32 km from Maloyaz, 12 km from Turnaly. == References == Category:Rural localities in Salavatsky District
title: Ayskaya
